    "doc": "SAM D21 Xplained Pro Evaluation Kit",
    "title": "SAM D21 Xplained Pro Evaluation Kit Reference Application Examples",
    "content": "This repository contains the MPLAB® Harmony 3 reference applications developed on SAM D21 Xplained Pro Evaluation Kit. | Getting Started | AC Sleepwalking Application built with ARM GCC Toolchain | . Note: . The applications in this repository are an alternative source of reference involving integration of multiple technologies, extending hardware capabilities and demonstrating specific MCU features. Peripheral/Technology specific applications are available in technology repositories like csp, core, usb, net, audio, gfx_apps, etc . ",
